    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and represents the pinnacle of its model year. It has been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a flawless exterior with zero scratches or dents and an interior that still looks and smells brand new. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a smooth engine and transmission that perform exactly as they did the day it left the showroom. Every feature and electronic component works perfectly, making this an ideal find for a collector or a buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
